race.comment: BY THE WAY (8) debuts for the Laming yard and has looked very sharp at the trials. Maps well and Lloyd stays aboard. Finds a winnable assignment and a bold effort is on the cards. PROPHET OF DESTINY (3) debuts and the rails gate is a plus. Showed ability in his recent Doomben trial and will get every chance jumping from an inside barrier. BRITANNIA ROSE (7) resumes and has shown enough in decent maidens to consider. has trialled twice and Ceejay Graham continues her association with the filly. CAPTAIN CASHE (1) debuts and has placed both trials. Has an awkward gate but he should run well regardless.
